.TH PRODBOX_users 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-users \- Operator-invited user management
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox users
.SH DESCRIPTION
Operator-facing Keycloak user management surface for the Phase 8 invite flow.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBinvite\fR
Invite an operator-owned user by email
.TP
\fBlist\fR
List operator-managed users
.TP
\fBrevoke\fR
Disable or delete an operator-managed user
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox users invite operator@example.invalid\fR
Invite a new operator-owned user.
